		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>2 Monument Yard. London</placeName></p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><date>29<hi rend="sup">th</hi> August 1861</date></p>
			<p rend="align(center)">The <placeName>London</placeName> Committee for the Appointment of a</p>
			<p rend="align(center)">Minister to the <hi rend="underline"><placeName>Sydney</placeName></hi> Hebrew Congregation</p>
				<p>Sir I forward you by this mail a copy<lb/> of the Jewish Chronicle of the <date>23<hi rend="sup">rd</hi></date> inst&#44;<lb/> containing our advertisement for<lb/> a minister to the <placeName>Sydney</placeName> Congregation&#44;<lb/> and am directed to request you to<lb/> insert the same in your next<lb/> publication.</p>
				<p rend="indent(1)">I shall feel obliged if you<lb/> will be kind enough to forward<lb/> me <del>a</del> two copies of the Occident in which<lb/> the advertisement appears&#44; and also</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>the account&#44; informing me at the<lb/> same time through what channel<lb/> I shall pay it for you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Your Obed Servant</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">G. L. Lyon</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Secy.</p>
				<p>The <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Editor Occident.</p>
		</body>
